                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4_1133">
                           <locus target="#172v">-172v</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="ar">Mas'ala about the unlawfulness for the master to vilify his disciples; fawā'id about Abū Ḥanīfa's and al-Ḥakīm al-Tirmiḏī's vision of God and about an invocation for forgiveness.</q>
                           <note>
                              <p>
                                 Mentioned
                              : <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS0520IHA">الترمذى , محمد بن عيسى</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                 Mentioned
